            "readonly": false,
            "desc": "Process incoming ALGO revenue from protocol fees.\nSplits the payment:   - buyback_pct% (default 90%) stays in contract for buyback-and-burn   - remainder goes to the operations address\nThe buyback ALGO accumulates until execute_buyback is called (which would swap on a DEX in production).",
