            "readonly": false,
            "desc": "Withdraw accumulated buyback ALGO for off-chain DEX swap.\nIn production, this would be replaced by an on-chain DEX integration (Tinyman, Pact, etc.). For now, the creator can withdraw ALGO to perform the swap manually and then call execute_burn with the purchased CORTEX.\nOnly callable by the application creator.",
